message.content:
You are implementing Task 1 of the Digital Loyalty Card App. 

**Context:** We are building a B2B2C loyalty platform. This is the very first task — creating the monorepo structure from scratch. Working directory is C:\Users\User. The project will live at C:\Users\User\loyalty-app.

**Prerequisites verified:** Node v20.20.0, pnpm 10.30.2

**TASK: Monorepo Scaffold with Turborepo**

Execute these steps IN ORDER. Do NOT skip any. Create all files with the exact content specified.

**Step 1: Create monorepo root**
```bash
cd /c/Users/User && mkdir -p loyalty-app && cd loyalty-app && git init && pnpm init
```

**Step 2: Create pnpm-workspace.yaml**
```yaml
packages:
  - "apps/*"
  - "packages/*"
```

**Step 3: Create turbo.json**
```json
{
  "$schema": "https://turbo.build/schema.json",
  "tasks": {
    "build": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"],
      "outputs": [".next/**", "!.next/cache/**", "dist/**"]
    },
    "dev": {
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "lint": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"]
    },
    "typecheck": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build"]
    }
  }
}
```

**Step 4: Create packages/shared/package.json**
```json
{
  "name": "@loyalty/shared",
  "version": "0.0.1",
  "main": "./src/index.ts",
  "types": "./src/index.ts",
  "dependencies": {
    "typescript": "^5.7.0"
  }
}
```

**Step 5: Create packages/shared/src/types/index.ts** with ALL these types:
```typescript
export type ProgramType = 'stamp' | 'points';
export type DiscountType = 'percentage' | 'fixed' | 'freebie';
export type ValidationMethod = 'qr' | 'nfc' | 'manual';
export type TransactionType = 'stamp_add' | 'points_add' | 'reward_redeem';
export type CustomerTier = 'bronze' | 'silver' | 'gold' | 'vip';
export type MerchantPlan = 'free' | 'pro' | 'business';
export type CampaignStatus = 'draft' | 'scheduled' | 'sent' | 'cancelled';
export type NotificationType = 'campaign' | 'reward_available' | 'expiration_warning' | 'proximity' | 'welcome' | 'referral';

export interface Merchant {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  logo_url: string | null;
  address: string | null;
  category: string | null;
  plan: MerchantPlan;
  subscription_status: string;
  stripe_customer_id: string | null;
  created_at: string;
}

export interface LoyaltyProgram {
  id: string;
  merchant_id: string;
  type: ProgramType;
  name: string;
  stamp_goal: number | null;
  points_per_euro: number | null;
  reward_description: string | null;
  expiration_days: number | null;
  is_active: boolean;
  created_at: string;
}

export interface Reward {
  id: string;
  program_id: string;
  name: string;
  description: string | null;
  points_cost: number | null;
  stamps_required: number | null;
  discount_type: DiscountType;
  discount_value: number;
  is_active: boolean;
  created_at: string;
}

export interface Customer {
  id: string;
  email: string;
  name: string | null;
  phone: string | null;
  push_token: string | null;
  preferred_language: string;
  created_at: string;
}

export interface CustomerCard {
  id: string;
  customer_id: string;
  program_id: string;
  current_stamps: number;
  current_points: number;
  tier: CustomerTier;
  last_activity: string;
  created_at: string;
}

export interface Transaction {
  id: string;
  card_id: string;
  type: TransactionType;
  value: number;
  validated_by: ValidationMethod;
  created_at: string;
}
```

**Step 6: Create packages/shared/src/index.ts**
```typescript
export * from './types/index';
```

**Step 7: Create .gitignore**
```
node_modules
.env
.env.local
dist
.next
.expo
*.tsbuildinfo
.turbo
```

**Step 8: Create .nvmrc**
```
20
```

**Step 9: Create apps directory (empty placeholder)**
```bash
mkdir -p apps
```

**Step 10: Install Turborepo**
```bash
cd /c/Users/User/loyalty-app && pnpm add -D turbo -w
```

**Step 11: Run pnpm install from root to link workspaces**
```bash
cd /c/Users/User/loyalty-app && pnpm install
```

**Step 12: Commit**
```bash
cd /c/Users/User/loyalty-app && git add . && git commit -m "chore: scaffold Turborepo monorepo with shared types"
```

IMPORTANT: Create ALL files. Do not skip steps. Verify the commit succeeds at the end.

